                              Temperature at which dew forms.
                           </para>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row valign="top">
                        <entry colname="col1">
                           <para>
                              Humidity
                           </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
                           <para>
                              Percentage of moisture in the atmosphere.
                           </para>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row valign="top">
                        <entry colname="col1">
                           <para>Vent</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="col2">
